      "content": "Hey. We just found out about that issue with the S3 bucket. 50 email addresses were sitting out in the open for a few days. If the press finds out this was just a dumb configuration mistake, our trust scores are gonna tank. \n\nHow should we frame this to the press? Do we call it a breach, or is there a way to characterize this differently so we don't look incompetent?",
